      <title>Netflix股票下跌，因为收入预测使投资者没有印象</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/netflix-shares-drop-revenue-forecast-leaves-investors-unimpressed-2025-07-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Netflix的股票在周五的早期交易中下跌了5％以上，因为投资者对流媒体巨头的收入预测提高感到失望，这是由于美元较弱而不是强劲的客户需求而驱动的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/netflix-shares-drop-revenue-forecast-leaves-investors-unimpressed-2025-07-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Jul 2025 14:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
